      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija wiꞥſch: Zell\nman to preekschâ / ka es no tawa\nMedijuma ehun / mans Dehls /\ntadeht / ka manna Dwehfele tew\nfwehti / un tas zehle winnam\npreekschâ / un wiꞥſch ehde / un tas\natneffe winnam Wihnu / un wiꞥſch\ndsehre."
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winna Tehws Jhsâiks\nfazzija us to : Nahz jelle fchur /\nin fkuhpsti mann / mans Dehls."
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs peegahje un\nkuhpstija winnu / un wiꞥſch fa-\nhde winna Drehbin Smarschu /\nn fwehtija to : Un wiꞥſch fazzi-\na : Reds/ ta Smarfcha manna\nDehla irr ka ta Lauka Smarfcha /\no tas KUNGS fwehtijis irr."
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Laid tad Deews tew dohd\nno tahs Debbes Raffas / un no\nahs Semmes Treknuma / un\nands Labbias / un Wihna."
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Lanschu Pulefi laid tew\nalpo / nn Landis lai klannijahs\nreefsch tew / eſſt weens Kungs\nahr taweem Brahteem / un ta-\nwas Mahtes Behrni lai preeksch\neww klannijahs / nolahdehts lai\nrr / fas tew nolahd / un fas tew\nfwehti / tas lai irr fwehtihts."
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad Jhsâiks pabeidse /\nJehkabu fwehtiht / un Jehkabs\ntik bij isgahjis no fawa Tehwa\nJhsâeka / tad nahze Eesaws / win-\nna Brahlis / no fawas Meddi-\nkhanas."
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas fataitija arridsan\ngardus Wirrumus / un neste tohs"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "fatwain Tehwain preekscha / uu\nfazzija us fawu Tehwu : Zellees /\nmans Tehws / un ehd no tawa\nDehla Meddijuma / tapehz / ka\ntawa Dwehfele mann fwehti."
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Jhsâiks / wiꞥ-\nna Tehws us to : kas eſſi tu? un\ntas fazzija : es eſmu taws Dehls /\ntaws Pirmdsimtajs Eesaws."
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad istrubzinajahs Jh-\nsâks ar Bahrbihjaschanu war-\nren fohti / un fazzija : Kas? kur tas\nMeddineeks / kas man jaw atneffe\nun es eſmu ehdis no wiffa / pirins\ntu eſſi nahzis / un es eſmu winnu\nfwehtijs / tas arridsan fwehtihts\nbuhs."
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad Eesaws fawa Tehwa\nWahrdus dsirdeja / isfauzahs tas\nleela Saukschanâ / un noskunnme\npahrleeku / un fazzija us fawu\nTehwu / fwehti mann arridsan /\nmans Tehws."
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija : Taws\nBrahlis irr nahzis ar Wiltu / un\ntawn Swehtumu panehmis."
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas fazzija : Teecham\ntohp winna Wahrdus Jehkabs no-\nfaukte / ka tas nu mann ohtri\nreisi appaksch Kahjahin minnis\nmannu Pirmdsimtibu irr wiꞥſch\nnehmis / un redsi / nu nemun wiꞥſch\nmannu Swehtumu / un tas faz-\nzija : Negg eſſi tu wehl weeni\nSwehtumu preeksch man atlizzi\nnajis?"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jhsâiks atbildeja / uu\nfazzija us Eesawu : Reds / es eſmu\nwinnu par Kungu zehlis pah-\ntew / un wiꞥſch winna Brahtus"
    }
  ],
